---
title: Greek Salad With Herbed Chicken & Feta  Cucumber, Grape Tomatoes, Almonds & Yogurt Dill Dressing
description: A fresh, crisp Greek salad is welcome on our table any time of year, especially when paired with juicy seared garlic-oregano chicken cutlets. You’ll serve the chicken atop a colorful salad of mixed greens, cucumber, and grape tomatoes tossed with briny feta and tangy yogurt-dill dressing, then sprinkle with nutty almonds for crunch.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66ba35bbfb4859096c8b61fd-01c31d09.jpeg
